short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A music bot for whatsapp web

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Now you can listen to songs with your pals on whatsapp's web app too.
Just ask your friends to install the extension, have fun vibing with them on whatsapp's web app.
Commands:
?p / ?play <song_name/ song's_youtube_url> : To play a song (Note : if a song is already playing, then requested song will be added to the queue.)
?p <youtube_playlist_url> /?pl <youtube_playlist_url> : To play songs from a playlist.
?s / ?fs : To skip the current song (Note : use these commands alternately to skip, entering same command will only work once)
?v : To pause the song.
?stop : To clear queue and stop playing songs.
